This is an application designed to centralize data about TV shows and possibly movies.

It will be able to scrape data from multiple sources to input to it's datastore about tv episodes.

Users will be able to create a list of their favorite shows and be able to view when new episodes of those shows will be airing.
  Users should also be able to track what episodes they have watched as to keep track of their progress of particular tv shows.

Potential for social interaction
  Have friends share their favorite shows and their progress 
    Could *ping* friends to have discussions around a particular episode
  